              "free_text": [
                " The activation curve and the cross-section",
                "curve for the reaction Ni58(gamma,n)Ni57 have been",
                "determined from threshold (12.0 MeV) up to 21.0 MeV.",
                "Nickel disks were irradiated in the center of the",
                "X-ray beam from the University of Saskatchewan 24-MeV",
                "betatron at a fixed distance from the target. The",
                "disks were irradiated at different maximum betatron",
                "energies, the irradiation procedure being the same",
                "for all disks."
              ]
            }
